# NeutroFilter (Open Source)

**NeutroFilter** is a privacy-first, browser-based tool that rephrases health, disability, or legally sensitive language into neutral alternatives. It is designed to help individuals communicate clearly while protecting their dignity and privacy.

This tool runs 100% in your browser. No data is tracked, collected, or stored.

